com.orsoncharts.data

Class DefaultKeyedValues<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.orsoncharts.data.DefaultKeyedValues<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    KeyedValues<T>, Values<T>, java.io.Serializable

    public final class DefaultKeyedValues<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements KeyedValues<T>, java.io.Serializable
    A list of (key, value) pairs.

    This is the basic structure of the data required for a pie chart.

    NOTE: This class is serializable, but the serialization format is subject to change in future releases and should not be relied upon for persisting instances of this class.
    See Also:
